---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
---

<div class="hero">
  <h1>안녕하세요, Hanson Kim입니다</h1>
  <p>개발, 기술, 그리고 생각들을 공유하는 공간입니다.</p>
</div>

<section class="tags-section">
  <h2>태그</h2>
  <div class="tags-cloud">
    {%- for tag in collections.tagList -%}
    {%- set tagCount = collections[tag].length if collections[tag] else 0 -%}
    {%- if tagCount > 0 -%}
    <a href="/tags/{{ tag | slugify }}/" class="tag-cloud-item">
      {{ tag }} <span class="tag-count">({{ tagCount }})</span>
    </a>
    {%- endif -%}
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="recent-posts">
  <h2>최근 포스트</h2>
  <ul class="post-list">
    {%- for post in collections.posts | reverse -%}
    <li>
      <article>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <time datetime="{{ post.data.date | dateDisplay }}">{{ post.data.date | dateDisplay }}</time>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </article>
    </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</section>
